run commands:
> npm init
> npm install --save react react-dom
> npm install --save-dev html-webpack-plugin webpack webpack-dev-server babel-core babel-loader babel-preset-react


setup following pages:
- app/index.html
- app/index.js
- .babelrc
- webpack.config.js

add to 'package.json' scripts:
  "production": "webpack -p"
  "start": "webpack-dev-server"

run commands:
> npm run production
--> This creates the Dist(index.html, index_bundle.js) directory.

install React Router:
> npm install --save react-router@2.0.0-rc5

install axios (for making https requests to APIs from node server, etc)
> npm install --save axios

check local file works on browser:
browser -> (ctrl + o)

check works on localhost:8080
> npm run start

-------------------
Extensions
-------------------
Animations:
> npm install --save react-addons-css-transition-group
> npm install --save-dev css-loader style-loader

Radium:
> npm install radium

Reflux:
> npm install --save redux
> npm install --save react-redux
> npm install --save-dev redux-devtools

React-Bootstrap:
> npm install react-bootstrap --save
